* Instructions on migrating to v2:
---
copy images/* to public/images/*
copy audio/* to public/audio/noaa/*
copy meteor/audio/* to public/audio/meteor/*

* Include ramfs handling in Ansible (and whatever is left over from install.sh).
* Update webpanel links for images to new image paths (above).
* Update scripts for audio and image directory adjustments (above) in scripts/.
* Update install_and_upgrade.sh script for handling webpanel content update.
* Create way to handle future database migrations.
* Run schedule script at the end of the installation if there are no jobs scheduled.
* Update NOAA_OUTPUT and METEOR_OUTPUT in scripts for new location.
